data.description: Enjoy the comfort and serenity of this beautiful move-in ready 3/2 home on 1 acre in Yulee. Built in 2019 this home features an open floor plan with crown moulding, a great kitchen, gas stove, gas logs fireplace, 10 KW generator, covered front porch, back porch and a back deck in shaded backyard.  Constructed with 2x6 exterior walls with extra insulation. Two wells, a water treatment system. New AC in 2023. No HOA, No CDD, you can park your boat and RV on this property. Zoned OR (deed restricted, no horses)  Two storage sheds on the property. Convenient to Amelia Island, Fernandina Beach, State Parks, golfing, fishing and more. Only a 15 minute drive to JAX airport. Don't miss this opportunity to make this lovely property your home.
